install net-snmp net-snmp-libs net-snmp-utils(for snmp manager)
install net-snmp-utils(for agent)
edit the file /etc/snmp/snmpd.conf 
need to edit the line "com 2sec notConfigUser default public"

rocommunity mysnmp1! 192.168.127.1 (rocommunity means read only, community string, ip of monitoring server)(for siem perspective ip of siem server)
restart the snmpd service.

test from local host: snmpwalk -v2c -c public localhost
                      snmpwalk -v 2c -c public -O e 127.0.0.1
                     
test from snmp agent side (from siem side):
                      snmpwalk -v 2c -c public -O e 172.0.25.160(ip of snmp manager, ie. ip of machine whose monitoring should be done)
                      snmpwalk -v 2c -c public -O e IP_OF_fortigate_400E (command from fortisiem side.)
                      
                      
